    <criterion testable="true">`PaneChannel` type literal union is STILL exactly `'workspace' | 'context' | 'conversation' | 'safety'` (no 5th channel). `PaneChannelEventMap` interface STILL maps exactly those 4 channels. `PaneEventBus.ts` `_channels` constructor STILL creates exactly 4 Sets.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">New optional fields for the new discriminants are added under dedicated comment blocks (`// ── streaming fields ──`, `// ── files_staged / file_selected fields ──`) with full JSDoc tying each field to the relevant discriminant per the existing wizard_step pattern. No `any` types used; `unknown` acceptable for genuinely polymorphic payloads.</criterion>
