    <criterion testable="true">Exhaustive-switch audit recorded in `notes/task-016-exhaustive-switch-audit.md`: every `switch (event.type)` callsite over `WorkspacePaneEvent` / `ContextPaneEvent` is enumerated with file path + line range + handling outcome (either new no-op cases added OR explicit ignore documented).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Static subscriber smoke-test sample of 5+ existing subscribers (`bus.subscribe` / `usePaneEvent`) recorded in task notes; each confirmed to narrow on known literal before discriminant-scoped field access, so unknown new types fall through harmlessly.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">BFF publish-size delta = 0 MB recorded in task notes (no BFF code change in this task).</criterion>
